# Firebase secrets — keep service-account JSON OUT of the repo (full project
# access). google-services.json itself is shipped inside every APK we
# distribute, so committing it here doesn't leak anything new — and EAS Build
# needs it from git to embed the FCM Sender ID into the build.
!apps/mobile/google-services.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json

# Google Play service account (EAS Android submit) — full Play Console access, NEVER commit
play-service-account.json
eas-play-*.json
*service-account*.json

